Market Snapshot: Apple clashes with energy to save earnings season 
MarketWatch Sunday 25th October, 2015 
Expected strong profits from Apple Inc. and consumer-based companies go up against a rash of weak energy sector results this week in a battle to try to save the S&P 500 from a projected earnings loss for the quarter. U.S. stocks finished up their...
